<p>The production of Kourtney And Kim Take Miami will take place in and around the Miami area as Kardashian sisters attempt to manage their DASH Miami store and take in some fun in the sun. Taking care of Kim's Kitty; New Persian cat Mercy is sure to get some attention in the coming season.  This season is expected to receive around 2 million viewers per episode.  DASH Miami get ready!</p>

